  "3210350": {
    "name": "Vampire Survivors: Ode to Castlevania",
    "steam_appid": 3210350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吸血鬼幸存者们一路狩猎，立下战功无数；在与贝尔蒙特家族联手后，目标终于近在眼前。终于能抓到那只吸血鬼了……应该吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日落月升之时，德古拉城堡暗潮汹涌。泥人、鬼魂和跳蚤男等魑魅魍魉倾巢出动，正邪大战再度爆发。用一系列新登场的吸血鬼杀器屠戮魔物，用血战杀出一条破灭之路，挽救这个即将万劫不复的世界。幸存者们，阴影已经降临，切勿视而不见，你们的任务才刚刚开始！现在情况很严重，还不快开足音量嗨起来。欢迎来到吸血鬼幸存者的恶魔城，宝贝<strong>！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/4457bf478fe707cc002b67e21c0a425c.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/cf2bcc2cd53c8d5f8499313656c2e520.poster.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/cf2bcc2cd53c8d5f8499313656c2e520.webm?t=1731510096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/cf2bcc2cd53c8d5f8499313656c2e520.mp4?t=1731510096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诅咒之夜太可怕了，尤其是对下列角色而言：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>贝尔蒙特家族 -</strong> 最爱鞭子的吸血鬼猎人世家，包括西蒙、里希达、特雷沃甚至索妮娅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>贝尔南堤斯家族 -</strong> 秘法家族历史上的女巫世家。赛法、洋子甚至夏洛特·欧琳和玛丽亚·雷纳德等远房亲戚都已准备好了法术书。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>其他英雄 -</strong> 不仅仅是乔纳森和夏洛特，还有乔纳森·莫里斯和约翰·莫里斯？！从夏诺雅到艾利克·利卡德，囊括众多出色的盟友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/dae49fa0b32d3a290134a9262d40319e.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/aa00cb7b91b997b98a0f551b0790b6c8.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗邪恶并非易事：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鞭子 -</strong> 很多鞭子，多到数不过来（有八种）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法术 -</strong> 元素魔法终于亮相《吸血鬼幸存者》。一系列灵感来自于《迷宫回廊》、《白夜协奏曲》和《夺还的刻印》的法术在此登场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔法武器 -</strong> 不是寻常的剑，而是阿鲁卡多的剑。还有阿鲁卡多的枪、盾牌等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>射弹 -</strong> 还记得莫里斯投掷标枪和铁球的时候吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>刻印 -</strong> 突剑、沃尔突剑、梅利欧突剑以及众多不是突剑的狠活，没开玩笑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/fd8921f786f9717c04449d413b198935.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中一些角色是最广为人知的多面手，掌握不同的能力，因此以这些角色游玩原版游戏可能会有千差万别的体验。强迫你使用这些角色却又不许换武器就显得笨笨的了，所以……好吧，我们会强迫你使用武器，但仅限一小会儿！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以为每个角色解锁至少一项武器选取；例如，晨星将允许你选取任意鞭子作为好邻居贝尔蒙特的起始武器：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/97674fb31b188f7bfca43177eed3db92.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/ba08788ad718ef1986037d972a1f62ac.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/cad8d7ad1d56ed52a84124442331958b.poster.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/cad8d7ad1d56ed52a84124442331958b.webm?t=1731510096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/cad8d7ad1d56ed52a84124442331958b.mp4?t=1731510096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽秘杀机，只待客来：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凶险的秘密和头目齐齐扎堆，构成《吸血鬼幸存者》有史以来的最大地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210350/extras/210059ab1b7b6af175765e955b125725.avif?t=1731510096\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔城混音曲目的典藏集。一贯为《吸血鬼幸存者》作曲的Daniele Zandara和Filippo Vicarelli，联手粉丝最爱的Evelyn Lark和Keygen Church，共同呈上一场听觉盛宴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♫ Vampire Killer、Bloody Tears、Simon's Theme、Leon's Theme……主题曲多不胜数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♫ Moonlight Nocturne、Lost Paintings、Dance of Pales——以你从没听过的新版本呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♫ Aquarius、The Beginning、Divine Bloodlines……一切都在彰显恶魔城的经典曲风。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♫ An Empty Tome、Invitation of a Crazed Moon、Pitch Black Inruption，以及同系列的最新热门曲目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♫ Amber Scenery、Sarabande of Healing、Jaws of a Scorched Earth——这些只是冰山一角，还有很多神秘曲目！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此之外，我们还借用了恶魔城原作的几十首原创曲目。由于曲目众多，我们为此重新设计了音乐选择界面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后的点睛之笔：某个男人。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语",
